---

<section id="about" class="h-[80vh] flex items-center bg-zinc-950 py-8">
  <div class="container px-6 mx-auto flex flex-col md:flex-row items-center md:items-start text-center md:text-left">
    <div class="md:w-1/2 flex justify-center scroll">
      <div class="relative w-92 h-92">
        <div class="absolute inset-0 rounded-full bg-gradient-to-r from-cyan-500 to-purple-500 blur-xl opacity-50 animate-pulse"></div>
        <div class="relative w-full h-full rounded-full overflow-hidden border-4 border-purple-500">
          <div class="w-full h-full bg-zinc-800 flex items-center justify-center text-5xl font-bold">
            <img src="perfil.jpg" alt="Paisaje bonito" class="w-full h-auto object-cover" />
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="md:w-1/2 flex flex-col items-center md:items-start scroll">
      <h2 class="text-5xl md:text-6xl ml-8 font-bold mb-6 bg-clip-text text-transparent bg-gradient-to-r from-cyan-400 to-purple-500">
        About me
      </h2>
      <p class="text-zinc-400 mt-3 text-xl px-8">
        ðŸ‘‹ Hi, I'm <strong>Samuel Sotomayor</strong>, a <strong>Computer Engineering student</strong> with a strong interest in <strong>web development</strong>.  
        I'm passionate about <strong>creating engaging projects</strong> and <strong>learning new technologies</strong> to constantly improve my skills. 
        My goal is to become a <strong>full-stack developer</strong>, specializing in building <strong>dynamic, efficient, and scalable web experiences</strong>.
      </p>
      
      <p class="text-zinc-400 mt-3 text-xl px-8">
        Beyond coding, soccer is one of my biggest passions, I love playing and following my favorite teams.  
        I also enjoy video games, especially titles like Counter-Strike, Fortnite, and FC25.  
      </p>
      <p class="text-xl md:text-2xl mt-3 ml-8 text-center font-bold bg-clip-text text-transparent bg-gradient-to-r from-purple-400 to-cyan-500">
        Skills
      </p>
      <p class="text-zinc-400 text-xl px-8">
        React - Nextjs - MongoDB - MySQL - Nodejs
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  @keyframes futuristicFade {
  from {
    opacity: 0;
    transform: translateY(30px) scale(0.9);
    filter: blur(15px);
  }
  to {
    opacity: 1;
    transform: translateY(0) scale(1);
    filter: blur(0);
  }
}

.scroll {
  animation: futuristicFade 1s cubic-bezier(0.25, 0.46, 0.45, 0.94) forwards;
  animation-timeline: view();
  animation-range: entry 0% cover 40%;
  }
</style>

  
  
